ch.zhaw.iamp.rct.graph

Class Mass

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.zhaw.iamp.rct.graph.Mass

  • public class Mass
extends Object
    A Mass is part of NetworkGraphs and represents a node, which may connect several springs.

    The complete robot arm and its mass-spring network are technically connected via masses. In order to handle logically different masses programmatically different, masses have to be of a specific Mass.Type. The default is Mass.Type.NETWORK, therefore is a normal network mass.
